OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man, 86, who
OL,4,Cdied after being hit by e-bike
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died after
OL,7,Fbeing hit by an e-bike have paid
OL,8,Ftribute to the "loveable" grandfather.
OL,10,FBart O'Hare, 86, died from his
OL,11,Finjuries after the incident in , on 22
OL,12,FMarch.
OL,14,Fwere called to the scene on Accrington
OL,15,FRoad at 4.23pm after a report that an
OL,16,Fe-bike had crashed into a pedestrian.
OL,18,FMr O'Hare later died in hospital.
