OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man, 86, who
OL,4,Cdied after being hit by e-bike
OL,6,FIn a statement, his family said: "Bart
OL,7,Fwas such a kind and loveable dad,
OL,8,Fbrother and grandad who has been taken
OL,9,Faway from family and friends in such a
OL,10,Ftragic manner.
OL,12,F"As a family we would like to thank
OL,13,Fall the emergency services involved
OL,14,Ffor all their work.
OL,16,F"Bart you will be missed by so many,
OL,17,Fmay you now rest in peace."
