OL,4,Cdied after being hit by e-bike
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing serious injury by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving and failing to stop
OL,9,Fat the scene of an injury road traffic
OL,10,Fcollision.
OL,12,FHe has since been released on bail as
OL,13,Fpolice inquiries continue.
OL,15,FThe e-bike has yet to be recovered,
OL,16,Fpolice said, in an appeal for
OL,17,Finformation.
