OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to man, 86, who
OL,4,Cdied after being hit by e-bike
OL,6,FSergeant Paul McCurrie, Lancashire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "We're particularly
OL,8,Finterested in hearing from anyone who
OL,9,Fmay have seen a dark-coloured Sur-ron
OL,10,Fe-bike, similar to the one pictured,
OL,11,Feither being ridden or stored, that
OL,12,Fmatches this description."
OL,14,FAnyone with information has been asked
OL,15,Fto contact police on 101 quoting log
OL,16,F0952 of 22 March, or email
OL,17,FSCIU@lancashire.police.uk.
